{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_13_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 3話 いつかは本当に好きな人と",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影が始まる少し前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Shortly before the CM shoot begins",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "着替えてきましたけど……\n私のドレス姿、おかしくないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've finished changing‚ but…\ndoes this dress look strange on me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いや……よく似合ってるよ。とても綺麗だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… it suits you well. You look beautiful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2722708702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.4756947677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか……なんだか\n面と向かって言われると照れますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… somehow‚\nhearing you say it to my face is embarrassing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2644865036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.4285904725
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜……表情が硬いが、もしかして緊張しているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei… your expression is stiff. Are you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4285904725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、緊張しますよ。ウエディングドレスを着て\n撮影するだけでも緊張するのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I'm nervous. Just wearing a wedding dress\nfor a shoot is enough to make me tense…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2460024834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4018355847
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、誤解を解くために\n私の関係者みんなを結婚式場に招待するなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but to think we'd invite all my acquaintances\nto the venue just to clear up the misunderstanding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0793358167,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4764.207982999998,
          "startTime": 40.8435437997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.8435437997
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "学校の友達に、ご近所さん、ダンススクールの関係者\nタケミヤの店長や店員さん、商店街の人達まで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "School friends‚ neighbors‚ dance school staff‚\nthe Takemiya manager and staff‚ even the shopkeepers…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2793358167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.319439141
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "だが、これで誤解も解けるはずだ\n実際に撮影を見れば変な噂はもう広まらないさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this should clear up the misunderstanding.\nOnce they see the actual shoot‚ the rumors will stop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさんも『大勢に祝福される幸せな花嫁』を\n撮れるから参加は歓迎だって言ってくれましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The staff said they're happy because they can film\n\"a happy bride blessed by many‚\" so they welcomed it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.130398496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.0002736886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "百歩譲ってそれはいいとして、どうして最前列の\n一番目立つ席に私の両親と兄が座っているんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if I overlook that‚ why are my parents and brother\nsitting in the most prominent seats in the front row?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8461286966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.5349401633
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "新婦の関係者が一番前に座るのは普通じゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't it normal for the bride's family to sit in the front?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5349401633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.5435141564
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "もう、{user}さんまで！\n私は新婦じゃありません！　これは撮影です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ even you‚ {user}!\nI'm not the bride! This is a shoot!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.060036564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんなんて私のライブにだって滅多に来ないのに\nどうして今日に限って断らないのよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My dad hardly ever comes even to my live shows‚\nso why didn't he decline just for today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.060036564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.638367812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、娘の晴れ姿を間近で見たかったんだよ\n俺も少しは気持ちが分かる気がするな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure he wanted to see his daughter's finery up close.\nI think I can understand that feeling a little bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.0267124177
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "だから！　晴れ姿じゃありません！\nこれはただの撮影です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you! It's not my \"finery\"!\nThis is just a shoot!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1694438618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.3146915596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "家族の目の前で結婚式の撮影をするなんて\nほとんど罰ゲームじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Filming a wedding ceremony right in front of my family\nis basically a punishment game‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9694438618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "お母さんなんて、私のウエディングドレス姿を見て\n涙ぐんでいたんですよ。結婚する訳じゃないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Mom saw me in this wedding dress‚\nher eyes started welling up. Even though I'm not getting married…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9027771951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.3128784657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……久しぶりの家族全員での集まりが\nこれで本当に良かったのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… I wonder if it's really okay for our\nfamily reunion to be like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7027771951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.742878898
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ\nみんな楽しんでいるみたいだし、いいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ now.\nEveryone seems to be having fun‚ so it's fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "まるで他人事みたいに言ってますけど\n余裕があるのも今の内ですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say that like it's someone else's problem‚\nbut that calm won't last for long.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0243838311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.7034438451
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "さっきスタッフさんから提案されたんです\nせっかくだから結婚式と同じ段取りで撮影しようって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The staff just made a suggestion to me earlier.\nThey want to film it in the exact same order as a real wedding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9910504978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "最初は、私がお父さんにエスコートされて\nみんなに祝福されながらバージンロードを歩くんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ I'll be escorted by my father\nand walk down the aisle while being blessed by everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.6910504978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.2631172181
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "その後、新郎と一緒に誓いの言葉を述べて\n指輪の交換をするところを撮りたいそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ I'll exchange vows with the groom\nand they want to film the ring exchange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.7243695896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.0415962857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "結婚式を本番さながらに再現するのか……\n面白そうだが、新郎は誰がやるんだ？",
      "translations": {
